JD 3:

Job Responsibilities 



Procurement
• Lead vendor development & relationships. Create alternate vendor pipeline for better quality & cost considerations
• Drive timely RM/PM sourcing decisions to ensure on time manufacturing runs
• Reduce Cost with strong negotiations as scale of the business multiplies Demand Planning Process
• Lead the demand & supply planning (SNOP) process along with GM - Manufacturing & Quality Head to drive clarity for rolling 3 months in terms of demand & supply plans.


Supply
• Daily, weekly, monthly despatch co-ordinations for 3PL partners, Market places & all Q-com hubs. To ensure fill rates >98% at all times
• Embed technology solutions for easy of tracking & insight creations to streamline the process


Leadership & Systems
• Build a small, high-performing team as the business scales to ₹150 Cr+.
• Create and institutionalize SOPs, audit frameworks, and process discipline.
• Be a thought partner to the Founder on supply & procurement strategy, speed maximization & cost optimization.

